sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant API as FastAPI Router
    participant Room as RoomService
    participant Repo as RoomRepository

    Client->>API: POST /rooms { room_number, display_name }
    API->>Room: openOrJoinRoom
    alt 房號不存在
        Room->>Repo: create room + host P1
    else 房號已存在且未滿
        Room->>Repo: append player next slot
    end
    Room-->>API: RoomSnapshot
    API-->>Client: 200 RoomSnapshot
